227
00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:58,720
Wu Shiguang!

228
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:25,720
Wu Shiguang, bangun! Wu Shiguang!

229
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:29,600
Wu Shiguang.

