bangun.

233
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:52,880
Wu Shiguang?

234
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,600
Anda melebih-lebihkan diri anda!

235
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,800
Wu Shiguang, bangun!

236
00:25:23,320 --> 00:25:24,840
Wu Shiguang, bangun.

237
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:26,760
